-and-Community/Waste-and-Recycling/Recycling-and-Waste-Disposal/Recycle-Markets'),('Hide & Seek Children\'s Market','Hide & Seek Children\'s Market is a unique display of beautifully crafted children’s clothing, accessories, toys, décor, furnishings and everything in between. Our stallholders display creations that are skilfully hand-crafted or designed by artistic and independent locals who are passionate about creating high quality children’s style products.','Miami State High School','2017-08-26 09:00:00','2017-08-26 13:00:00','Gold Coast','General Events','http://www.hideandseekmarket.com.au',0,'Markets','http://www.goldcoast.qld.gov.au/hide-seek-childrens-market-41527.html'),('Art, craft and food markets','There are numerous markets on the Gold Coast showcasing food and hand-made art and crafts from the region.','Kurrawa Park, Old Burleigh Road, Broadbeach','2017-08-06 08:00:00','2017-08-06 14:00:00','Gold Coast','General Events','Www.goldcoast.qld.gov.au',0,'Markets','http://www.goldcoast.qld.gov.au/thegoldcoast/art-craft-markets-22942.html'),('Art, craft and food markets','There are numerous markets on the Gold Coast showcasing food and hand-made art and crafts from the region.','Hellenic Function Centre (grounds), Crombie Avenue, Bundall','2017-08-04 17:00:00','2017-08-04 21:00:00','Gold Coast','General Events','Www.goldcoast.qld.gov.au',0,'Markets','http://www.goldcoast.qld.gov.au/thegoldcoast/art-craft-markets-22942.html'),('The Collective Markets','TheCollective Markets are a South Bank must-do experience while in Brisbane. They feature plenty of cool trinkets and goodies that you won\'t find anywhere else including arts, crafts, homewares, collectibles, exotic items, designer fashion, handmade jewellery and much more.','South Bank Parklands','2017-08-04 17:00:00','2017-08-04 21:00:00','Brisbane','General Events','www.brisbane.qld.gov.au',0,'Markets','https://www.brisbane.qld.gov.au/whats-on/type/markets#/?i=1'),('Young Designers Market','The Young Designers Market features some of Brisbane\'s best up-and-coming designers and artists selling a range of fashion and accessories, jewellery, homewares, object design furniture and arts. The markets are generally held on the first Sunday of every month from 10am-4pm.','The Young Designers Market features some of Brisbane\'s best up-and-coming designers and artists selling a range of fashion and accessories, jewellery, homewares, object design furniture and arts. The markets are generally held on the first Sunday of every month from 10am-4pm.','2017-08-06 08:00:00','2017-08-06 16:00:00','Brisbane','General Events','www.brisbane.qld.gov.au',0,'Markets','https://www.brisbane.qld.gov.au/whats-on/type/markets#/?i=1'),('Michael Muir\'s Disappearing Act','Inspired by the coastal landscapes, regional towns and rolling hills of the Sunshine Coast, Michael Muir\'s latest exhibition, Disappearing Act, is an amalgamation of various landscapes observed during his recent travels through the towns of Montville, Maleny and Noosa Heads. Muir\'s unique take on a picturesque region oozes a holiday vibe.','an Murphy Gallery','2017-07-31 08:00:00','2017-07-31 18:00:00','Brisbane','General Events','www.visitbrisbane.com.au',0,'Exhibition','http://www.visitbrisbane.com.au/information/articles/arts-and-entertainment/art-exhibitions-in-brisbane?sc_lang=en-au');
